  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The experience of labor for a woman can be rewarding but can be traumatic. Medical clowning
      may alleviate the potential for trauma.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      The investigators plan to administer questionnaires to women who will agree to host a clown
      during their labor and to compare the feedback to those from women who did not.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
